ğŸ¯ Summary
The Tokenized Marketplace is a Hedera-based platform that transforms physical assets into digital NFTs and enables co-funding via lending tokens. It is modular, auditable, and designed for phased growth. The MVP implementation includes all core flows â€“ asset creation, lending, ownership tracking â€“ and is ready for testing and deployment.

This documentation serves as a complete guide for frontend, backend, and smart contract developers to continue or build upon the system.





